+/* ==================== DATA-DRIVEN LAYER (v64) ====================
+   1) roDue     — likelihood a customer orders again SOON (hot list)
+   2) feedback  — capture ratings/comments, feed them into risk & recovery
+   3) AI planner — after a CSR logs a reply, the AI decides the next move
+   Every DB call is best-effort: if a table isn't created yet, the app still
+   runs on local data and simply shows less — never an error. */
